Lorna's Silence;;69;;85;;R;;Lorna (Arta Dobroshi), a young Albanian woman living in Belgium, has hopes of opening a cafe with her boyfriend, an itinerant worker who visits when he can. She marries Claudy, a local junkie, to secure legal residency and collaborates with Fabio (Fabrizio Rongione), a low-life cab driver who arranges a hefty payoff for her to marry a Russian mobster. Lorna wants to divorce Claudy; but Fabio wants him to overdose. She knows nothing of the threatening underworld in which she will be enmeshed.;;Drama;;Jean-Pierre Dardenne,Luc Dardenne;;2008;;Arta Dobroshi,Jérémie Renier,Fabrizio Rongione,Alban Ukaj,Morgan Marinne,Olivier Gourmet,Anton Yakovlev,Grigori Manoukov,Mireille Bailly;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lornas_silence